## Output shape

```json
{
  "flags": {
    "c": "policy.yaml",
    "step": "build",
    "trace": "true"
  },
  "config_path": ".witness.yaml",
  "config_digest": {
    "sha256": "..."
  },
  "config_content": {
    "run": {
      "step": "build",
      "attestations": ["git", "environment"]
    }
  },
  "working_directory": "/workspace"
}
```

All fields are `omitempty`; absent fields mean the corresponding source was missing or unreadable.
